      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 02:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行政策变动震动市场，日本股市出现 2016 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/japan-s-topix-enters-correction-as-yen-strength-hits-exporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市出现 2016 年以来最大跌幅，基准东证指数较 7 月份高点下跌逾 10%，受紧缩货币政策影响，日本这个全球表现最好的市场之一陷入动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/japan-s-topix-enters-correction-as-yen-strength-hits-exporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：日本股市跌幅扩大，创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对美国经济和科技公司健康状况的担忧加剧，全球股市抛售加剧。日本股市因预期国内将进一步收紧货币政策而暴跌，进一步加剧了市场情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
